{
  "texts": [
    "Additional improvements through attention mechanism designs and contrastive learning approaches would help optimize the process of sentiment classification.",
    "F. Aspect-Sentiment-Opinion Triplet ExtractionStructured aspect-opinion-sentiment triplets that originate from Bangla product reviews form the final outcome of the system.",
    "E-commerce sentiment analysis becomes more interpretable through the triplets which provide detailed sentiment measurements from product evaluations.",
    "V. RESULT ANALYSISA comprehensive evaluation of different deep learning and transformer-based models for Aspect-Based Sentiment Triplet Extraction (ASTE) takes place in this section for Bangla product reviews.",
    "The combination of BanglaBERT + XGBoost forms an ensemble model which receives assessment against baseline systems."
  ]
}